These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, chestnut, azure, coral
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Color   | azure | chestnut | white | coral |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
City: venice, nizza, berlin, marseilles
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| City   | venice | berlin | nizza | marseilles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, pony, frog
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Pet   | pony | hedgehog | rabbit | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, davidoff, vegafina, chaman
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Cigar   | vegafina | havana | davidoff | chaman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, august, february
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | august | march | february | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, june, december
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3       |     4     |
| Birthday   | december | june | january | august |

